          <msContents>
            <summary>Manuscript used for private or public recitation and prayer containing a series of mantras in thirteen verses dedicated to a form of the Hindu goddess called Indrākṣī and associated with Dūrgā and Lākṣmī. Text is attributed to the figure Puraṃdara Ṛṣi in the incipit (f. 1r).</summary>
            <textLang mainLang="san">In Sanskrit</textLang>
            <msItem>
              <title>Indrākṣīstotra</title>
